Constant DLL_SUFFIX

1.0.0 Â· Source 
pub const DLL_SUFFIX: &str;
Expand description

Specifies the filename suffix, if any, used for shared libraries on this platform. An example value may be: ".so", ".elf", or ".dll".

The possible values are identical to those of DLL_EXTENSION, but with the leading period included.
